प्रादेशिकप्रसारः

  • Hiraṇyakeśī (rare)
  • Vaikhānasa (one specific class)
  • Vādhūla (May survive in KL)
  • Bhāradvāja (Extinct)
  • Agniveśya (a micro-class in TN)
